{
  "stem": "3012.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then it happened, in 1940, that a friend of my parents came up with the idea that there was a French convent in Budapest called Notre Dame de Sion, that's-- who-- which is running the equivalent of a high school, plus language and secretarial school, in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they would be more than willing to take new students.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They couldn't have less cared about religion, per se, because they didn't even ask.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were not forced to 'convert,' quote, unquote-- nothing of that sort.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Religion didn't even come to-- to be a problem.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was really an oasis during those times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I was staying with friends in Budapest--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, not that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My parents were not involved in Zionism.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- we-- they have-- I-- I remember there were-- there were meetings by the Keren Kayemeth, and there was another--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Keren Kayemeth.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, Keren Kayemeth, the Jewish National Fund.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish National Fund.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, they were-- they were contributors to that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then there-- they-- they had subscription to Zionist newspapers, but they were not active-- that's what I meant-- in the movement.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the beginning of the grammar school-- from between six and ten-- there really was not anything-- anything too bad about it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But gradually, as the war broke out in-- the Second World War, in 1939.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went to school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then my parents were rather strict about my homework, and I-- I tried to do my best.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I probably should have done much more than I did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I learned-- when I started at gymnasium I started also learning languages.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the-- in the gymnasium that was also co-ed, we started Latin the first year.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was extremely difficult, and everybody hated it because of the grammar and all that.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
